  <title>Derivatives</title>
  <introduction>
    <p>
      <xref ref="chapter_limits"/> introduced the most fundamental of calculus topics:
      the limit.
      This chapter introduces the second most fundamental of calculus topics:
      the derivative.
      Limits describe <em>where</em> a function is going;
      derivatives describe <em>how fast</em> the function is going.
    </p>
  </introduction>

